    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"greener future\" part sounds pretty definitive. Do people actually agree that the transition is a good thing if it means more job losses in places like Western PA? I'm wondering if the economic impact on the coal communities is being weighed fairly against the solar stuff.",
