      "content": "you called it an \"outdated, polluting industry\" though. isn't that a bit one-sided? if someone thinks coal is vital for the local economy and energy security, saying it's just \"outdated\" makes it sound like their concerns aren't even valid. can you explain why you're framing it that way instead of just saying it's a different viewpoint?",
